# ITC-Hotels-Revenue-Optimization-PowerBI
ðŸ”¹ Project Overview
This project is a comprehensive Power BI dashboard designed to analyze and optimize
revenue performance for a luxury hospitality business inspired by ITC Hotels.
The dashboard provides deep insights into financial performance, occupancy trends,
room category contribution, booking behavior, and cancellation patterns over a
three-month period.
The primary objective is to enable data-driven decision-making for hotel management
by tracking key hospitality KPIs such as Revenue, ADR, RevPAR, Occupancy Rate,
Week-over-Week (WOW) growth, Month-over-Month (MOM) growth, and Cancellation Rate.

ðŸ”¹ Business Problem
Hotel management teams often struggle to identify revenue leakages, understand room
category performance, and track the impact of cancellations on overall profitability.
This project addresses:
- Which room categories generate the most revenue
- How occupancy and RevPAR vary over time
- The financial impact of cancellations
-  Week-over-week and month-over-month performance trends

ðŸ”¹ KPIs & Metrics Used
- Total Revenue Generated
- Revenue Realized
- Average Daily Rate (ADR)
- Revenue Per Available Room (RevPAR)
- Occupancy Rate
- Week-over-Week (WOW) Growth
- Month-over-Month (MOM) Growth
- Cancellation Rate
- Lost Revenue due to cancellations

ðŸ”¹ Dashboard Pages
1. Financial Overview
   - Revenue Generated
   - ADR and RevPAR
   - Monthly Revenue Trends
   - Cumulative Revenue
2. Occupancy Analysis
   - Occupancy Rate by Property and Room Category
   - Occupancy Trends by Date
   - WOW and MOM Occupancy Changes
3. Performance Analysis
   - Room Category Revenue Contribution
   - Lead Time Analysis
   - Length of Stay (ALOS)
   - Weekly Growth Trends
4. Cancellation Analysis
   - Cancellation Rate by Property and Room Category
   - MOM and WOW Cancellation Trends
   - Lost Revenue due to Cancellations

ðŸ”¹ Data Model & Approach
- Built a star schema using fact and dimension tables
- Created a custom calendar table for time intelligence
- Used DAX measures for all KPIs
- Applied conditional formatting for performance indicators
- Ensured consistent UI/UX using ITC Hotels inspired color palette

ðŸ”¹ Tools & Technologies
- Power BI
- DAX
- Data Modeling
- Time Intelligence
- GitHub for version control

ðŸ”¹Dataset
- Simulated hospitality dataset inspired by ITC Hotels
- Covers bookings, revenue, room categories, occupancy, cancellations
- Time period: 3 months (daily & weekly granularity)

