ðŸ”¹ Key Insights
- Elite and Premium room categories contribute the highest share of revenue
- Occupancy remains around 43â€“50% across properties with clear weekday-weekend patterns
- Cancellations account for a significant revenue leakage (~25%)
- Revenue growth shows volatility across weeks, highlighting demand seasonality

ðŸ”¹ Outcome
This dashboard enables hotel management to:
- Optimize room pricing strategies
- Reduce revenue loss from cancellations
- Identify high-performing properties and room categories
- Monitor growth trends at weekly and monthly levels

